channel.title: Eclipse throwing random errors?
channel.description:
[center]basically i dled a brand new server from the dl section.
And before i even had a chance to edit it or do anything i set it up in eclipse and it is saying theres 100s of errors.
though i know something must be wrong sice this is the 2nd server to do this to me.
Not be a noob but could someone tell me how to set up a server in eclipse in case im doing something wrong.
Atm i created a new java project in my workspace, imported the server and BAM 100s of erros, wtf? [/center]
